  "subject": "Review docker profiles",
  "commit_message": "Review docker profiles\n\nThis change prevents to generate cps-service docker image when\nrunning maven-stage-master job by:\n\n* Disabling jib plugin by default\n* Enabling jib plugin only for docker profiles\n\nDocker images are also renamed with service suffix for consistency.\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-175\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Sakoto <bruno.sakoto@bell.ca>\nChange-Id: I37fa2f98479b3340ff1ec68b9b6e3167c2dba8ff\n",
